{"pageProps":{"problem":{"id":"t5-train-2","grade":"7","semester":"up","category":"有理数","title":"针对训练2：绝对值最值问题","difficulty":4,"tags":["绝对值","最值"],"content":"已知 $|a - 4| + |a + b| = 0$，则 $a = $ ______，$b = $ ______；其中正确的结论序号是 ______。\n\n① $|b| < 0$；② $|a| < |b|$；③ $2 - |a| < 0$；④ $2a - b > a + b$。","steps":[{"title":"解绝对值方程","content":"由 $|a - 4| + |a + b| = 0$，非负数和为 0，则每项为 0\n\n$a - 4 = 0 \\Rightarrow a = 4$\n$a + b = 0 \\Rightarrow b = -4$","formula":"a = 4, \\quad b = -4"},{"title":"验证结论","content":"① $|b| = 4 > 0$，错误\n② $|a| = 4 = |b|$，错误\n③ $2 - |a| = 2 - 4 = -2 < 0$，正确\n④ $2a - b = 8 + 4 = 12$，$a + b = 0$，$12 > 0$，正确","formula":"\\text{答案：③④}"}]},"id":"t5-train-2"},"__N_SSG":true}